Titolo: Minions of Mirth

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Minions of Mirth is a role-playing game for Mac OS X and Microsoft Windows by American studio Prairie Games, Inc. The game includes both a single-player and a massively multi-player mode. There were two editions of the game: a free version and a paid version which opened additional character abilities.It was written and produced by Josh Ritter and Lara Engebretson from 2003, with a launch in December 2005. Online servers from Prairies Games ceased in September 2017, due to a hard drive failure; the official servers closed on 22 September 2017, but single-player and at least one private server still run.

Genere: MMORPG

Valutazione: N/A
